::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 504001001: Config/Level/Mission/5040010/Act/Act504001001.json-->
::'''Iason:''' No grand adventure is complete without a dromas! Hey there, stranger. Judging by that glint in your eyes, you're a fan of dromas just like me, right?
::'''Iason:''' I'm Iason, the manager of this caravan "Argo." All dromas in Okhema are my good friends, and I'm the one who gave each of them a name.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} You named all the dromases?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504001004-->
:::'''Iason:''' Exactly. Asterion, Euphemus, Castor, Pollux, and the mightiest of them all, Heracles &mdash; all solid names.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} What does your caravan trade in?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504001006-->
:::'''Iason:''' Everything! Argo used to just carry bulk goods, but times have been rough, so we've expanded our business.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504001007-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504001007-->
::'''Iason:''' Things aren't as calm as they used to be. If you need to move anything into Okhema or find something rare, Argo's your safest bet. Trust me, Heracles is just as dependable as the Chrysos Heirs!
;(Subsequent interactions)
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 504001002: Config/Level/Mission/5040010/Act/Act504001002.json-->
::'''Iason:''' Legend has it that in the Era Chrysea eons ago, there was this massive airship called Argo, whose captain was also named Iason. Iason sailed the world with his dromas buddies, helping out those in need, much like the Chrysos Heirs do these days.
::'''Iason:''' Friend, I can see that spark in your eyes &mdash; the yearning for adventure with your dromas buddies. Am I right?
:<!--Ends the current performance-->
:<!--Open NPC Menu-->
:{{DIcon|Shop}} What rare stuff do you have?
::'''Iason:''' Feel free to pick out anything that catches your eye. Sadly, my stock's running low these days, and all I've got left are dromas souvenirs.
:<pre>{
	"$type": "RPG.GameCore.VerifyInteractingEntity",
