:{{DIcon}} You seem well-versed in dromas.
::'''Iason:''' You've found the dromas master! Down at the workshop, they all call me the Dromas Idol Producer! When it comes to those marvelous creatures, I'm your go-to person! Whose story catches your eye?
::<!--Custom String Trigger: Wait_Option_504001003_31-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: Wait_Option_504001003_31-->
::{{DIcon|Talk}} Let's talk about Asterion.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504001103-->
:::'''Iason:''' Asterion has been on quite the journey, starting from the time they were chosen as the first living being under the protection of {{Rubi|Kephale|Worldbearing Titan}}, all the way to when the young dromas began exploring the world.
:::'''Iason:''' Unfortunately, those arduous adventures have taken their toll on Asterion, causing a deep anxiety disorder known as {{Rubi|agoraphobia|Reluctance to Meet People}}.
:::'''Iason:''' If you ever catch Asterion seeking solace in their {{Rubi|sanctuary|barn}}, please remember they're just an old hero looking for a quiet retirement.
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} Let's talk about Euphemus.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504001107-->
:::'''Iason:''' Euphemus is a close comrade of Asterion's, and the mightiest dromas after Heracles. We once made it to Corchis just before the black tide hit and managed to salvage its legendary treasures...
:::'''Iason:''' Four crates packed with rubber ducks!
:::'''Iason:''' Yeah, that was an unlucky trip, I admit. I was hoping for some real treasures in those crates, but those rubber ducks barely covered our costs.
:::'''Iason:''' I should have just popped open those crates right there and let those ducks ride the black tide...
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} Let's talk about Castor and Pollux.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504001112-->
:::'''Iason:''' Castor and Pollux are a pair of young dromases. Castor is a bit older than Pollux, and neither has faced any life-or-death adventures yet.
:::'''Iason:''' However, in preparation for their future business, I've concocted a cool pitch that could make them the ultimate duo! Let me share it with you!
:::'''Iason:''' Through the {{Rubi|Chrysalis of Gold|Romance Titan}}'s grace, we present to you a rare pair of twin dromases, Castor and Pollux! Hailing from {{Rubi|Georios|Earth Titan}}, these two boast impressive teamwork and confidence, much like two Chrysos Heirs gearing up for their heroic fate!
:::'''Iason:''' ...Lady Aglaea won't consider this false advertising, right?
::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Talk}} Let's talk about Heracles.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504001117-->
:::'''Iason:''' Aha! You've finally brought up my favorite, Heracles! Let me tell you, he's not just the strongest and smartest dromas around today &mdash; Even if Sabany came back from the black tide, no dromas there would outshine him!
:::'''Iason:''' Heracles has been my loyal partner through countless impossible tasks. Among them, I've dubbed the toughest twelve challenges he faced as The Twelve Trials of Heracles.
::;(If {{cx}}<!--SubMission Started: 304002002-->)
::::'''Iason:''' Eager to hear more about his adventures? I've penned an epic just for Heracles. Here, take a copy.
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::;(If {{cx}}<!--SubMission not Started: 304002002-->)
:::;(Return to previous option selection (cloneCheckString))
::{{DIcon|Exit}} Wish you all the best in your business.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504001121-->
:::'''Iason:''' Thank you! Feel free to swing by and grab anything that catches your eye! Catch you later!
:::<!--Ends the current performance-->
:{{DIcon|Exit}} Wish you all the best in your business.
::'''Iason:''' Thank you! Feel free to swing by and grab anything that catches your eye! Catch you later!
::<!--Ends the current performance-->
